title: Who are you, sir?"
body: Who are you, sir?"The Bishop answered:--"My name is Bienvenu Myriel.""Bienvenu Myriel?I have heard that name.Are you the man whom the people call Monseigneur Welcome?""I am."The old man resumed with a half-smile"In that case, you are my bishop?"
author: 0x2aB2199F0026D555CA583b95123f49b1478851f0
